title: Episode 128: The Survival Story of Susan Walters Kuhnhausen
description:
She had a job she loved, a lust for life, and was on her way to newfound freedom. But then she came home from work and found herself faced with a man hellbent on taking her life. Was this some random attacker or was the motive something more sinister?
